17, "username": "mrtallon", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/mrtallon", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0e7c/c4c2/504517_mini.png?m=1730084761", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0e7c/c4c2/504517_normal.png?m=1730084761", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0e7c/c4c2/504517_large.png?m=1730084761", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0e7c/c4c2/504517_xlarge.png?m=1730084761", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0e7c/c4c2/504517_xlarge.png?m=1730084761", "created": 1597822330, "last_modified": 1730084761}, "last_reply_by": "victorc", "last_touched": 1730350253, "title": "汽车有必要贴车衣吗", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1084910", "created": 1730267444, "deleted": 0, "content": "明年家里要添崽子了，二人世界变三口之家\r\n\r\n打算购置一台理想 L7 中配或高配，主要生活在成都市区，偶尔去川西自驾\r\n\r\n请问有必要贴车衣吗\r\n\r\n最近刷视频全看的是给理想贴车衣，说车漆较薄，以我现在的车来看，确实在车门处有不少细小的磕碰导致掉漆", "content_rendered": "<p>明年家里要添崽子了，二人世界变三口之家</p>\n<p>打算购置一台理想 L7 中配或高配，主要生活在成都市区，偶尔去川西自驾</p>\n<p>请问有必要贴车衣吗</p>\n<p>最近刷视频全看的是给理想贴车衣，说车漆较薄，以我现在的车来看，确实在车门处有不少细小的磕碰导致掉漆</p>\n", "last_modified": 1730348999, "replies": 98, "id": 1084910}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f854/54e8/422_large.png?m=1605263518", "name": "browsers", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f854/54e8/422_normal.png?m=1605263518", "title": "浏览器", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/browsers", "topics": 741, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Browsers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f854/54e8/422_mini.png?m=1605263518", "stars": 445, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 422, "parent_node_name": "software"}, "member": {"id": 541323, "username": "banlifeather4", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/banlifeather4", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2574/0edd/541323_mini.png?m=1692084886", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2574/0edd/541323_normal.png?m=1692084886", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2574/0edd/541323_large.png?m=1692084886", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2574/0edd/541323_xlarge.png?m=1692084886", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2574/0edd/541323_xlarge.png?m=1692084886", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2574/0edd/541323_xlarge.png?m=1692084886", "created": 1617702647, "last_modified": 1692084886}, "last_reply_by": "byby", "last_touched": 1730351145, "title": "我为什么选择 edge，而不用 chrome", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1085007", "created": 1730280352, "deleted": 0, "content": "edge 和 chrome 这两个浏览器犹豫了好久，才确定 edge 作为常用浏览器使用\r\n\r\n1. 日常用的网站，密码也都是在 edge 上记住的\r\n2. 最常用的插件也都是在 edge 上安装的\r\n3. 个人偏好设置也是集中在 edge 上\r\n4. 而且 edge 还有我最喜欢的功能 **双击关闭标签页**\r\n\r\n但 edge 作为微软的产品，一点分寸感都没有，总是莫名其妙的引导我做一些设置，比如微软接入的电商资讯，还有一次将我重新整理的标签页全弄丢了（就是完全没有了）\r\n\r\n刚刚看到 chrome 有一个小功能很吸引我，又开始犹豫了，到底 chrome 双击关闭标签页的功能该怎么设置啊？\r\nps：还有一点，我个人感觉 chrome 分寸感好一点", "content_rendered": "<p>edge 和 chrome 这两个浏览器犹豫了好久，才确定 edge 作为常用浏览器使用</p>\n<ol>\n<li>日常用的网站，密码也都是在 edge 上记住的</li>\n<li>最常用的插件也都是在 edge 上安装的</li>\n<li>个人偏好设置也是集中在 edge 上</li>\n<li>而且 edge 还有我最喜欢的功能 <strong>双击关闭标签页</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<p>但 edge 作为微软的产品，一点分寸感都没有，总是莫名其妙的引导我做一些设置，比如微软接入的电商资讯，还有一次将我重新整理的标签页全弄丢了（就是完全没有了）</p>\n<p>刚刚看到 chrome 有一个小功能很吸引我，又开始犹豫了，到底 chrome 双击关闭标签页的功能该怎么设置啊？\nps：还有一点，我个人感觉 chrome 分寸感好一点</p>\n", "last_modified": 1730282584, "replies": 92, "id": 1085007}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 27032, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913", "stars": 3047, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 443807, "username": "Bananana", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Bananana", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b64d/dac5/443807_mini.png?m=1729563383", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b64d/dac5/443807_normal.png?m=1729563383", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b64d/dac5/443807_large.png?m=1729563383", "created": 1569649485, "last_modified": 1729563383}, "last_reply_by": "godall", "last_touched": 1730324684, "title": "准备退了 m3 air 买 m4 的 Mac mini，想问下外接 ssd 推荐", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1084929", "created": 1730269608, "deleted": 0, "content": "现在的 mbp 也基本是外接显示器，看新的 mac mini 挺喜欢的，准备直接买 mac mini 了。\n准备买 24G 内存+256GB 的配置，想问下外接 ssd 有什么推荐或者成熟的方案吗？ mac 上的 app 能装到外接 ssd 上嘛？", "content_rendered": "现在的 mbp 也基本是外接显示器，看新的 mac mini 挺喜欢的，准备直接买 mac mini 了。<br />准备买 24G 内存+256GB 的配置，想问下外接 ssd 有什么推荐或者成熟的方案吗？ mac 上的 app 能装到外接 ssd 上嘛？", "last_modified": 1730269608, "replies": 75, "id": 1084929}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 224639, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 4259, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 161110, "username": "hfl1995", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/hfl1995", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "lageev", "btc": "", "location":